title: Airdrop for Sake Holders
body:
An airdrop would atract a lot of buyers and it would easily PUMP the coin price
10M Sake would be airdroped
The rewads will be proportional with the amount of Sake that wich one have, with a minimum reaward of 500 Sakes for the elegible people.
Requirements to be elegible:
-Have at least 1500 Sakes when the snapshot is taken
The snapshot will be taken 18st October, 15 UTC
The distribution will occur right after the snapshot

The airdrop will be spreaded along all social media
choices: Yes, I want to PUMP the coin and receive a lot of Sake
I liked the proposal but I would like some different conditions
